* Lambrecht, Ralph E.. &quot;A Wisconsin Legend: Ole Evinrude and his Outboard Motor,&quot; &quot;Wisconsin Magazine of History&quot;, vol. 89, no. 3, (Spring 2006), pp. 16–27.

