<doc id="780766" wikidata="Q4361143" url="?curid=780766" title="Ezzelini">
<text>The Ezzelini were a noble family in medieval Italy. The family was founded by Ecelo (Ezzelo), who received the fiefs of Romano d&#x27;Ezzelino and Onara
* Ezzelino I da Romano (died 1189), called &quot;il Balbo&quot;
** Ezzelino II da Romano (died 1235), called &quot;il Monaco&quot;, son of Ezzelino I
*** Ezzelino III da Romano (1194–1259), called &quot;il Tiranno&quot;, son of Ezzelino II
*** Alberico da Romano (1196–1260), son of Ezzelino II
*** Cunizza da Romano (born c. 1198), daughter of Ezzelino II</text><links>
